lzh_formatted:
  title: 寒松亭曲
  author: 張延祐
  language: lzh
  text: 月白寒松夜。波安鏡浦秋。哀鳴來又去。有信一沙鷗。
korean:
  title: 한송정곡
  author: 장연우
  language: kor
  text: |-
    한송정 밤에 달은 희고
    경포의 가을 물결은 잔잔
    슬피 울며 오고 가느니
    유신한 백구 하나
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0220_010_0040&viewSync=OT
english:
  title: Song of the Cold Pine Pavilion
  author: Zhang Yanyou
  language: eng
  text: |-
    The moon gleams white on this cold pine night,
    still waters mirror autumn at Gyeongpo.
    A mournful cry comes and goes—
    one faithful gull bears witness.
  footnotes:
    - Gyeongpo (경포) is a famous scenic lake in Gangneung, Korea, known for its beauty in autumn
    - The 'faithful gull' (유신한 백구) carries traditional symbolism of constancy and solitude in East Asian poetry
